      "message": "[Critical] Line 1919: syncConversationsWith() is documented and named as syncing with a specific peer, but bootstrap(conv-\u003eid()) re-bootstraps the whole conversation. For group conversations this can contact/fetch from unrelated members when the wake-up was caused by one peer, which is a privacy and performance regression. Route the sync to the requested member/device only, or add a peer-scoped bootstrap path before exposing this public API.\n```suggestion\n            pimpl_-\u003ebootstrap(conv-\u003eid(), uri);\n```",
